  <span id="freeText3001206497125400891" style="display:none">Gavin has two people in this world that make him feel loved; and neither of them are his parents. He is only truly happy when he is running, and soon that passion leads him to a new love-football. But when his star rises on the field, a new and dangerous game begins.<br /><br />Charles Mahoney has written a book that is so much more than just a sports story. It is a story about life; both the good and not-so-good parts. <br />Everything about Story of The Ghost is great-the writing, the characters, the story. Mahoney does it all beautifully and perfectly, and you are truly pulled into the story from the beginning. It is easy to read, and it is relatable. We have all followed the same path as Gavin in some way at some point in time, so we can completely understand where he is coming from. It's just great writing from page one!!<br />This is a book I highly recommend everyone to read...you will not be sorry and you may even see it change your life in ways you wouldn't even imagine!</span>
